        "content": "## Deliver a daily digest with Google Drive and Gmail hands-free\n\n**Tier:** Professional · **Difficulty:** Intermediate\n**Pattern:** Alerts (Reporting & Analytics)\n**Architecture:** validated input, branch on anomaly detected?.\n\nImport, add your credentials, then adjust parameters. Original WorkflowCrate template.",
